  <h5>Art in the Americas</h5>
  <hr />
  <p>Art history in the Americas began in pre-Columbian times with indigenous cultures. This category refers to arts by indigenous peoples in the Americas from ancient times to present day.  The indigenous peoples referred to include those of South America, Meso America, and North America, including Greenland.</p></div>
