  <h5>Art of Pacific Cultures</h5>
  <hr />
  <p>Art of Pacific cultures refers to those from the oceanic regions of present day Australia, Melanesia, Micronesia, and Polynesia, including areas as far as Hawaii and Easter Island.  Art from these peoples vary throughout different regions and cultures.  Themes of the supernatural and fertility are the most common.  Masks, tattoos, painting, petroglyphs, stone and wood carving, and textile are the most common art forms.</p></div>

